    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《星尘舰队》是一款突破传统的即时战略游戏。游戏以全息投影般的2D平面战场模拟星际战争，玩家将扮演新任联邦舰队指挥官，在浩瀚银河中书写属于自己的战争史诗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/4b526f1b282029668f382a2049c4a8c2.poster.avif?t=1756433600\" width=652 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/4b526f1b282029668f382a2049c4a8c2.webm?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/4b526f1b282029668f382a2049c4a8c2.mp4?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 瞬息万变，运筹帷幄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兵无常势，水无常形。我们独创的舰队指挥系统打破传统RTS桎梏，既保留战略深度又大幅简化操作。指挥官既能如臂使指般调度整支舰队，又能随时切换视角对单舰实施毫米级微操，在宏观布局与精密操作间无缝切换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/0f3b1158da939b1c7fc6327ddb14bab7.poster.avif?t=1756433600\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/0f3b1158da939b1c7fc6327ddb14bab7.webm?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/0f3b1158da939b1c7fc6327ddb14bab7.mp4?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 矛与盾的交响</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每艘战舰都是攻防一体的战争艺术品。三大属性攻击武器暗含相生相克之道——粒子束撕裂护甲，电磁脉冲瘫痪系统，量子鱼雷摧毁结构。对应防御系统如同精密交响：偏转护盾、反制力场、引力漩涡各展所长。指挥官需洞悉战场，调配最佳攻防组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/a2bcfd41c186fa8391a5980946924d09.poster.avif?t=1756433600\" width=618 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/a2bcfd41c186fa8391a5980946924d09.webm?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/a2bcfd41c186fa8391a5980946924d09.mp4?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 千舰竞发，各司其职</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从灵巧的护卫舰到遮天蔽日的航母，五大舰种构建起星际战争交响曲。驱逐舰是攻守兼备的中坚力量，巡洋舰的轨道炮可贯穿星海，航母释放的无人机群自成战术体系，而补给舰则是维系持久战力的生命线。唯有深谙舰队协同之道，方能在银河战场奏响凯歌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 生命、能量与弹药的博弈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三维资源系统重塑战略思维——弹药枯竭可能让巨舰沦为废铁，能量透支将关闭武器阵列，而护盾过载更会引发连锁反应。指挥官需在炮火纷飞中统筹整支舰队的资源循环，补给舰的每一次驰援都可能成为扭转战局的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 星河史诗，荡气回肠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们以电影级运镜呈现百年星战的壮阔画卷。每个关卡都是精心编排的太空歌剧，通过动态战场事件与多重叙事手段，让指挥官亲历改变银河命运的史诗时刻。当全息沙盘上的战术推演与文明存亡的宏大叙事交织，每个决策都将镌刻在星辰之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/1089b6a5bfec90337ea6d9332fe1ae1d.poster.avif?t=1756433600\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/1089b6a5bfec90337ea6d9332fe1ae1d.webm?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310330/extras/1089b6a5bfec90337ea6d9332fe1ae1d.mp4?t=1756433600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
